{"tid":975008,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"夢入面既記憶到底點分真假？","createTime":"2019-01-09T10:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T14:43:41.000Z","uid":26491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7afc2efdee03112924f016ee1deba320bd912605","tid":975008,"uid":26491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"唔我昶日發夢既時候都知道自己發夢，但我係好似遊戲角色咁跟著走，唔係發現左自己發夢就可以回都得嗰啲，最多係發現走勢唔啱既時候可以回頭重試一次咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近期越黎越多次係我夢入面發現呢個夢已經發過，而且有深刻記憶<br />\n<br />\n但到我訓醒既時候回憶我又完全唔覺有發過同一個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到我開始懷疑係咪有啲開始混淆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底點分真假既記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0227ecc59cc24a98dace9c42f93591da0101dd13","tid":975008,"uid":214692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b499cc7f4da196026635eba5109a1daaf0bcc176","tid":975008,"uid":24607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"你未整圖騰？"},{"pid":"6a7511b08d218ca5298b51bf9c00de158afe2fc7","tid":975008,"uid":175622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"多啲做 reality check.<br />\n你好似開始接觸 lucid dreaming 層面，reality check 可以幫你分清你而家係發緊夢定係喺現實，係現實同發夢都要做，每日當習慣每兩個鐘做一次。<br />\n<br />\n可以做嘅野有：<br />\n1. 數手指。夢裡面你唔會數得出隻手有5隻手指<br />\n2. 試下睇一啲你睇過既書或者notebook，總之有字嘅野。如果發夢，啲字會唔同左，或者直情睇唔到內容係咩。<br />\n3. 督自己手掌。發夢嘅話，你會督穿自己手掌，或者掂住但係感覺唔到。<br />\n<br />\n每次做 reality check, 唔可以淨係做一次就算，要連續做幾次例如睇字唔好淨係望一次就完，因為有時我地個腦會呃到我地一下。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以自己 Google 下 lucid dream reality check. 方法唔止呢三個。"},{"pid":"488e881df7a8a3ac9f091717730563a94cc6167d","tid":975008,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGjOx1O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGjOx1O.gif&h=40034998&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be4f619b41e39bf63480d28c6b4f461d90acf3f4","tid":975008,"uid":26491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488e881df7a8a3ac9f091717730563a94cc6167d","tid":975008,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGjOx1O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGjOx1O.gif&h=40034998&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"冇真實到咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}